text:
Hi everyone!

So glad to be here :relieved:

I'm Sanketee from Pune, India. I'm an Industrial psychologist who worked as an HR & Ops Manager at marketing agencies earlier and eventually took up content writing.
After a string of sucky episodes with my bosses (read: delayed payments, unrealistic expectations, eventual stagnation, etc.), I decided to start freelancing full-time.
I generally write for modern B2B SaaS and e-commerce brands that don't shy away from incorporating some personality in their brands.
If I'm not writing about these topics, you'll find me writing about mental health and wellness.

I'm here to connect with fellow writers and know more about the current happenings in the industry.
